{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/add-slideshow-shopify-no-apps","result":{"pageContext":{"id":1133,"date":"2021-09-06T02:22:28","date_gmt":"2021-09-06T02:22:28","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=1133"},"modified":"2021-09-11T05:21:20","modified_gmt":"2021-09-11T05:21:20","slug":"add-slideshow-shopify-no-apps","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/add-slideshow-shopify-no-apps/","title":{"rendered":"How to add a premium slideshow section to any theme (without apps)"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>The vast majority of the themes available on Shopify come, by default, with a slideshow section built in. Usually they do their job very well, offering a simple yet effective way to showcase products and promotions, which, fundamentally, is what any business need.<br><br>However, not all is a bed of roses: it is not rare to hear complaints about slideshows cutting off images on mobile, the text being right on top of the focal point of the image (and not being able to simply adjust it), or, really, just things looking off in general. <br><br>The image either going too much to one of the sides, the text covering up the model&#8217;s face or just some technical aspect beyond the user&#8217;s control quick transforms simple into complex.<br><br>Bearing this issue in mind, we have created a premium slideshow section that solves all of those issues. It is a section just like any other, so you can move it around, hide it and customize to your liking: it actually comes with 50+ customization options out of the box, with even more features being added all the time. Plus it works on <strong>any theme</strong> and it just takes a few seconds to install.<br><br>Here&#8217;s a live demo of this section working: <strong><a href=\"https://pandatests.myshopify.com/pages/slideshow\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">live demo (please click here)</a></strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-making-a-copy-of-your-current-theme\">Making a copy of your current theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before diving into the tutorial make sure you download the theme, so in case you face any issues you can easily revert back.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1514\" height=\"481\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png 1514w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-600x191.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-1200x381.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-downloading-the-slideshow-code-file\">Downloading the slideshow code file</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>To download the slideshow code &amp; read all of its features, please <a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/slideshow-section-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">click here</a>. (<a href=\"https://pandatests.myshopify.com/pages/slideshow\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">live preview</a>) </p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-step-1-opening-the-code-editor\">Step 1: opening the code editor</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>From your Shopify admin, navigate to&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Actions&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Edit Code</strong>.</li><li>Inside the <a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/slideshow-section-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">.zip you downloaded</a> you&#8217;ll find the following file: <strong>ezfy-slideshow.txt</strong>. Please open it.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-step-2-installing-the-section-in-your-theme\">Step 2: installing the section in your theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Under the folder <strong>sections</strong>, on the left side of your code editor, click on &#8220;Add a new section&#8221;.</li><li>Type exactly <strong>ezfy-slideshow</strong> and click on the green button &#8220;Create section&#8221;.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1372\" height=\"769\" class=\"wp-image-1143\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide1-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide1-1.jpg 1372w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide1-1-850x476.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide1-1-1200x673.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide1-1-768x430.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1372px) 100vw, 1372px\" /></li><li>Inside this new file that you created, delete everything. Make sure it&#8217;s blank and please <strong>don&#8217;t</strong> save just yet.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1574\" height=\"605\" class=\"wp-image-1145\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide1.1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide1.1.jpg 1574w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide1.1-850x327.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide1.1-1200x461.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide1.1-768x295.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide1.1-1536x590.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1574px) 100vw, 1574px\" /><br></li><li>Now that the file is empty, paste all the code from the file that you have downloaded on <em>step 1</em>, <strong>ezfy-slideshow.txt</strong>, and click on <strong>save</strong>. <br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1559\" height=\"815\" class=\"wp-image-1141\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide2.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide2.jpg 1559w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide2-850x444.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide2-1200x627.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide2-768x401.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide2-1536x803.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1559px) 100vw, 1559px\" /></li><li>Perfect! Now let&#8217;s add this section to your website. </li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-step-3-adding-the-section-to-your-website\">Step 3: adding the section to your website</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>At the top of your code editor, click on the button <strong>&#8220;Customize theme&#8221;</strong>.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1572\" height=\"590\" class=\"wp-image-1147\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide3.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide3.jpg 1572w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide3-850x319.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide3-1200x450.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide3-768x288.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide3-1536x576.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1572px) 100vw, 1572px\" /></li><li>On the left side, scroll all the way down until you find the button &#8220;Add section&#8221;. Click on it.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1182\" height=\"756\" class=\"wp-image-1149\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide4.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide4.jpg 1182w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide4-850x544.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide4-768x491.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1182px) 100vw, 1182px\" /></li><li>On the new dropdown that appeared, search for <strong>Ezfy Slideshow (PRO). </strong>You may need to click on &#8220;show more&#8221; to see all sections available.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1131\" height=\"735\" class=\"wp-image-1151\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide5.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide5.jpg 1131w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide5-850x552.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide5-768x499.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1131px) 100vw, 1131px\" /><br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1075\" height=\"749\" class=\"wp-image-1153\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide6.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide6.jpg 1075w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide6-850x592.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slide6-768x535.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1075px) 100vw, 1075px\" /></li><li>That is it! </li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Questions, issues or concerns? Please reach out to us at <strong>ezfycode@gmail.com</strong>, we&#8217;ll take care of it! </p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Add a gorgeous slideshow section to any theme by simply copying and pasting one single file. </p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1135,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[206,154,91],"image_alt":"","acf":[],"featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slideshow_2-850x478.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slideshow_2-200x200.png","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/slideshow_2-1200x675.png","post_count":0,"categories_names":["Blog"],"tag_names":["all themes","Code Tutorial","customizable"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1133"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/users/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"